                <ComponentExampleBox Title="ChoiceGroup with LabelTemplate" HTMLSourceCode="@example5BitChoiceGroupItemHtmlCode" CSharpSourceCode="@example5BitChoiceGroupItemCSharpCode" ExampleId="example5">
